The paper deals with video object segmentation, which is a topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The approach presented involves using machine learning algorithms such as R-CNN and Box2Seg, which fall under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses tracking algorithms, which are relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM).
